  "remarks": "Petropars Oilfield Services Company (POSCO) is a wholly-owned subsidiary of Petropars Iran, which is in turn a wholly-owned subsidiary of Petropars Ltd (PPL). PPL is wholly-owned by Naftiran Intertrade Company Ltd (NICO), which belongs to the National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC). NIOC is a State-owned company which provides support to the Government of Iran.",
